name: Horimon 005 蛇:SNAKE
description:
Meaning : Life, immortality, fertility, reclamation

Snakes shed their skin and grow bigger, they can also go a long time without eating. This makes the snake a symbol of life. Snakes are a very popular tattoo motif all over the world, like ouroboros or Asclepius' cane.
The lotus also has a meaning of life, since it blooms beautifully from muddy water.
